text: Homonoea ornamentalis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Heller in 1926. It is known from the Philippines.BioLib.cz - Homonoea ornamentalis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==Subspecies== * Homonoea ornamentalis mindanaonis Breuning, 1980 * Homonoea ornamentalis ornamentalis Heller, 1926 ==References== Category:Homonoeini Category:Beetles described in 1926
